data.description: Check out this great south central home waiting for its new owners! This 1950’s all brick 3+1 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom, one story home features original hardwood floors, large living room, spacious eat in kitchen, 3 bedrooms, an updated main floor bathroom, and main floor laundry. The basement features a nice sized living space, 1 non-conforming bedroom, half bath, and ample amounts of storage. Step outside to a 1.5 car detached garage. Plus, a large backyard perfect for entertaining, that has a new privacy fence that was recently installed. Scheduled your showing today!!
